embed.title: All Animals of Summoners Rift - League of Legends Wildlife Documentation
embed.description: Prof. Azir and his side-kick Teemo bring us some fascinating shots of the Summoners RIft. They caught nearly all animals of the new map on tape. And they claim to have the evidence for the existence of Bigfoot. Are the two researchers right with their assumptions?

body:
Hey Folks, 
ever wondered about the nicely animated animals in the new Summoners Rift? I nearly got them all in my new video. The first League of Legends Wildlife/ Animal Documentary :D 
Check it out, let me know if you already knew them all and what u think about my video.
